OL,6,FA 10-year-old schoolgirl from , whose
OL,7,Fmother is accused of murder, died from
OL,8,Fstab wounds to her chest, an inquest
OL,9,Fheard.
OL,11,FShay Kang was found dead at a house in
OL,12,FRobin Close at around 12.10pm on
OL,13,FMonday, March 4.
OL,15,FShay's mother and remanded in custody
OL,16,Fcharged with murder.
OL,18,FShe was remanded in custody until
OL,19,FApril 22.
