OL,6,FAt a short hearing at Black Country
OL,7,FCoroner's Court on Thursday, March 21,
OL,8,Fwas told Shay's cause of death had
OL,9,Fbeen established as stabbing injuries.
OL,11,FAdjourning the inquest until a date to
OL,12,Fbe fixed, Black Country area coroner
OL,13,FJoanne Lees said: "The death of Shay
OL,14,FKang was reported to the coroner by
OL,15,FWest Midlands Police.
OL,17,F"A post-mortem has been conducted and
OL,18,Fa medical cause of death has been
OL,19,Festablished as stab wounds to the
OL,20,Fchest."
