OL,6,FMrs Lees added: "I have been notified
OL,7,Fby the Crown Prosecution Service that
OL,8,Fa person had been charged with a
OL,9,Fcriminal offence in connection with
OL,10,Fthe death of Shay.
OL,12,F"On the evidence before me today, I am
OL,13,Fsatisfied that it is appropriate to
OL,14,Fformally open the inquest.
OL,16,F"I am going to suspend my coronial
OL,17,Finvestigation and adjourn the inquest
OL,18,Fpending the outcome of criminal
OL,19,Fproceedings."
