OL,6,FShay was a pupil at Brickhouse Primary
OL,7,FSchool, which paid tribute to the
OL,8,F"bright" child in a statement issued
OL,9,Fthrough West Midlands Police a day
OL,10,Fafter she was found dead.
OL,12,FThe school said: "Shay was a bright,
OL,13,Fhappy, fun-loving child who was well
OL,14,Fliked by all and she will be very
OL,15,Fsadly missed by everyone.
OL,17,F"School is the heart of the community
OL,18,Fand we have already begun working with
OL,19,Four children and staff to support them
OL,20,Ffollowing this devastating news."
